OL,3,CSharp rise in reported cases of sexual
OL,4,Charassment on London's transport system
OL,6,F"Sadly, we know that many women feel
OL,7,Fthat they have no option but to put up
OL,8,Fwith sexual harassment. That's not the
OL,9,Fcase: if someone is persistently
OL,10,Fbothering you and makes you feel
OL,11,Funsafe or uncomfortable, please text
OL,12,F61016 to report it.
OL,14,F"Our officers are on patrol 24/7 and
OL,15,Fcan meet trains at the next station.
OL,16,FIf it happens on the tube and you
OL,17,Fdon't have signal, you can speak to
OL,18,Fstaff or text us at the next station.
